      "notes": "Java/C++ GLR v2 drivers (GSS prefix sharing + SPPF; nextAst projection via getNextAst(); getSppfRoot()/getSppfSymbolCount()). error_repair_count>0 falls back to BacktrackingParser %Recover prosthesis (single tree). Other backends emit nextAst scaffolding only until a runtime driver ships."
